commit message: Try to fix problem with android opening the first preference-entry by default when displaying preferences while the intent is still null. Also apply better layout to preferences.

Issue 121: Added preference to 'Invert browsing articles', displays all articles when opening a category and all feeds when long-pressing it instead of the normal behaviour which is the other way round.
Added confirmation dialog to unsubscribe from feed

== Version 1.49 ==
* Added a preference to 'Invert browsing articles'
* Fixed problems with the new preference-dialog
* Added confirmation dialog to unsubscribe from feed
